    "updated_at": "2015-05-04T05:23:43Z",
    "body": "This is a bug of OS X, it seems that OS X didn't calculate the width of `°C` correctly. Setting title to other text works as expected.\n\nMore interestingly, following code works correctly:\n\n``` js\ntray.setTitle('19');\ntray.setTitle('19°C');\n```\n"
